Please. don't hurt me.
Please. please.

600
00:32:27.486 --> 00:32:28.946
Oh. God. Oh. God.

601
00:32:29.071 --> 00:32:31.698
[shushing] Don't be scared.

602
00:32:33.700 --> 00:32:36.869
It's like you told me.
"Death is a natural.

603
00:32:36.870 --> 00:32:38.663
