604
00:32:38.664 --> 00:32:42.042
I'll give you anything you want.

605
00:32:42.209 --> 00:32:44.086
A life of luxury.

606
00:32:44.211 --> 00:32:45.419
I'm good.

607
00:32:45.420 --> 00:32:49.799
