What about your son? Mm.

608
00:32:49.800 --> 00:32:52.386
Don't you want Harrison
to go to a good college?

609
00:32:52.511 --> 00:32:53.761
I'll give you enough money

610
00:32:53.762 --> 00:32:54.930
