Never utter my son's name again!

612
00:32:57.557 --> 00:33:01.144
Okay. Okay. Oh. God.

613
00:33:02.187 --> 00:33:03.688
[groans]

614
00:33:03.689 --> 00:33:05.439
None of this would've happened

615
