But my father
had a thing for justice.

624
00:33:36.388 --> 00:33:38.765
He taught me
to kill only bad people.

625
00:33:39.725 --> 00:33:42.894
So. I was intrigued
when I found Red's invitation.

626
00:33:43.020 --> 00:33:45.439
Your dinner

627
