Being around like-minded people.

630
00:33:59.036 --> 00:34:00.579
Oh. it was intoxicating.

631
00:34:00.704 --> 00:34:02.622
That's-that's-that's what
I always wanted.

632
00:34:02.748 --> 00:34:04.540
- I know.
- A place

633
00:34:04.541 --> 00:34:07.793
