I'm not going
in the blood slide box?

696
00:37:13.855 --> 00:37:15.147
Nope.

697
00:37:15.148 --> 00:37:16.441
You're not.

698
00:37:16.566 --> 00:37:21.195
Oh. God. Oh. God. [laughs] Yes.

699
00:37:21.196 --> 00:37:24.824
I knew you'd see it my way.

700
