702
00:37:30.872 --> 00:37:32.665
[whimpers]

703
00:37:32.666 --> 00:37:34.668
I am going to kill you.

704
00:37:34.793 --> 00:37:36.378
But-but you...

705
00:37:36.503 --> 00:37:39.756
