722
00:39:11.973 --> 00:39:14.600
<i>♪ I'm a woman's man.
no time to talk ♪</i>

723
00:39:14.601 --> 00:39:17.228
<i>♪ The music loud
and the women warm ♪</i>

724
00:39:17.354 --> 00:39:19.271
<i>♪ I've been kicked around
